<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Notification Prestataire - {{domainName}}</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .email-container {
            max-width: 650px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3A7B59 0%, #4a9968 100%);
            padding: 30px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            position: relative;
        }

        .logo-container {
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 20px 25px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .logo-image {
            max-width: 120px;
            height: auto;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 45px 35px;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #fffef7 0%, #fefdf5 100%);
        }

        .greeting {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            text-transform: capitalize;
        }

        .provider-title {
            color: #3A7B59;
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }

        .hours-notice {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF6B35 0%, #FF8A50 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 25px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 35px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.3);
        }

        .customer-info-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e8f5e8 0%, #f0f8f0 100%);
            border: 1px solid #3A7B59;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .customer-info-card h3 {
            color: #3A7B59;
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .customer-info-card p {
            color: #2d5f44;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 5px 0;
        }

        .reservation-card {
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 35px;
            margin-bottom: 35px;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            border: 1px solid rgba(58, 123, 89, 0.1);
        }

        .domain-name {
            color: #333 !important;
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none !important;
        }

        .wine-cellar-image {
            width: 180px;
            height: 180px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            object-fit: cover;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .reservation-details {
            width: 100%;
        }

        .reservation-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }

        .image-column {
            width: 50%;
            text-align: center;
            vertical-align: top;
            padding-right: 25px;
        }

        .details-column {
            width: 50%;
            vertical-align: top;
        }

        .details-grid {
            width: 100%;
        }

        .grid-row {
            width: 100%;
            margin-bottom: 18px;
        }

        .grid-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }

        .grid-cell {
            width: 50%;
            padding-right: 15px;
            vertical-align: top;
        }

        .grid-cell:last-child {
            padding-right: 0;
        }

        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            min-height: 24px;
        }

        .detail-icon {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 16px;
            height: 16px;
            margin-right: 8px;
            font-size: 14px;
            text-align: center;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            line-height: 1;
        }

        .detail-icon img {
            width: 16px;
            height: 16px;
            object-fit: contain;
            vertical-align: middle;
        }

        .detail-text {
            color: #444;
            font-weight: 500;
            line-height: 1.3;
            white-space: nowrap;
            overflow: hidden;
            text-overflow: ellipsis;
        }

        .detail-text.long-text {
            white-space: normal;
            font-size: 11px;
        }

        .price-row {
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            padding-top: 15px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .price-text {
            color: #3A7B59;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .description {
            clear: both;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }

        .preparation-checklist {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin-top: 25px;
        }

        .preparation-checklist h3 {
            color: #856404;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .checklist {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .checklist li {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 8px 0;
            color: #856404;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f5e79e;
        }

        .checklist li:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        .checklist li::before {
            content: "‚úì";
            background-color: #28a745;
            color: white;
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-right: 15px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: #3A7B59;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            clear: both;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .footer-table {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 500px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }

        .footer-left-cell {
            width: 70%;
            text-align: left;
            vertical-align: middle;
        }

        .footer-right-cell {
            width: 30%;
            text-align: right;
            vertical-align: middle;
        }

        .footer-logo-container {
            width: 100%;
        }

        .footer-logo-table {
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }

        .footer-logo-icon-cell {
            width: 50px;
            vertical-align: middle;
            padding-right: 15px;
        }

        .footer-logo-icon {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 5px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .footer-logo-icon img {
            max-width: 30px;
            max-height: 30px;
            width: auto;
            height: auto;
            display: block;
        }

        .footer-logo-text-cell {
            vertical-align: middle;
        }

        .footer-logo-text {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: white;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .footer-contact {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: white;
        }

        .domain-address {
            color: #999;
            font-size: 14px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .email-container {
                margin: 10px;
                max-width: none;
            }
            
            .content {
                padding: 30px 25px;
            }
            
            .reservation-card {
                padding: 25px 20px;
            }
            
            .reservation-table {
                display: block;
            }
            
            .image-column,
            .details-column {
                display: block;
                width: 100% !important;
                padding: 0 !important;
            }
            
            .image-column {
                margin-bottom: 25px;
            }
            
            .wine-cellar-image {
                width: 140px;
                height: 140px;
                margin: 0 auto;
            }
            
            .grid-table {
                display: block;
            }
            
            .grid-cell {
                display: block;
                width: 100% !important;
                padding: 0 !important;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
            }
            
            .detail-row {
                font-size: 13px;
            }
            
            .detail-text {
                white-space: normal;
            }
            
            .provider-title {
                font-size: 26px;
            }
            
            .footer-table {
                display: block;
            }
            
            .footer-left-cell,
            .footer-right-cell {
                display: block;
                width: 100% !important;
                text-align: center !important;
                padding: 10px 0;
            }
            
            .footer-logo-table {
                margin: 0 auto;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <!-- Header with Logo -->
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo-container">
                <img src="{{domainLogoUrl}}" alt="{{domainName}} Logo" class="logo-image">
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Main Content -->
        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">Bonjour {{providerName}}</div>
            
            <h1 class="provider-title">Invit√© attendu prochainement</h1>
            
            <div class="hours-notice">
                L'exp√©rience commence dans {{hoursBeforeEvent}} heure{{#if (gt hoursBeforeEvent 1)}}s{{/if}} !
            </div>
            
            <div class="customer-info-card">
                <h3>üë§ Invit√©</h3>
                <p><strong>{{eventName}}</strong></p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="reservation-card">
                <h2 class="domain-name">{{domainName}}</h2>
                
                <div class="reservation-details">
                    <table class="reservation-table">
                        <tr>
                            <td class="image-column">
                                <img src="{{serviceBannerUrl}}" alt="{{serviceName}}" class="wine-cellar-image">
                            </td>
                            
                            <td class="details-column">
                                <div class="details-grid">
                                    <!-- Row 1: Date/Time and Language -->
                                    <div class="grid-row">
                                        <table class="grid-table">
                                            <tr>
                                                <td class="grid-cell">
                                                    <div class="detail-row">
                                                        <span class="detail-icon"><img src="https://api.rosedesvins.co/v1/web/image/clock" alt="Clock"></span>
                                                        <span class="detail-text">{{eventDate}} - {{eventTime}}</span>
                                                    </div>
                                                </td>
                                                <td class="grid-cell">
                                                    <div class="detail-row">
                                                        <span class="detail-icon"><img src="https://api.rosedesvins.co/v1/web/image/language" alt="language"></span>
                                                        <span class="detail-text">{{selectedLanguage}}</span>
                                                    </div>
                                                </td>
                                            </tr>
                                        </table>
                                    </div>
                                    
                                    <!-- Row 2: Service and Duration -->
                                    <div class="grid-row">
                                        <table class="grid-table">
                                            <tr>
                                                <td class="grid-cell">
                                                    <div class="detail-row">
                                                        <span class="detail-icon"><img src="https://api.rosedesvins.co/v1/web/image/type-of-experience" alt="Experience"></span>
                                                        <span class="detail-text long-text">{{serviceName}}</span>
                                                    </div>
                                                </td>
                                                <td class="grid-cell">
                                                    <div class="detail-row">
                                                        <span class="detail-icon"><img src="https://api.rosedesvins.co/v1/web/image/clock" alt="Duration"></span>
                                                        <span class="detail-text">{{eventDuration}}</span>
                                                    </div>
                                                </td>
                                            </tr>
                                        </table>
                                    </div>
                                    
                                    <!-- Row 3: Participants and Wine Count -->
                                    <div class="grid-row">
                                        <table class="grid-table">
                                            <tr>
                                                <td class="grid-cell">
                                                    <div class="detail-row">
                                                        <span class="detail-icon"><img src="https://api.rosedesvins.co/v1/web/image/user" alt="Participants"></span>
                                                        <span class="detail-text">{{participantsAdults}} personne{{#if (gt participantsAdults 1)}}s{{/if}} (adultes)</span>
                                                    </div>
                                                </td>
                                                <td class="grid-cell">
                                                    <div class="detail-row">
                                                        <span class="detail-icon"><img src="https://api.rosedesvins.co/v1/web/image/wine-glass" alt="Wine"></span>
                                                        <span class="detail-text">{{numberOfWinesTasted}} vins</span>
                                                    </div>
                                                </td>
                                            </tr>
                                        </table>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                
                                <div class="detail-row" style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 11px;">
                                    <span class="detail-icon"><img src="https://api.rosedesvins.co/v1/web/image/euro-currency-symbol" alt="Payment"></span>
                                    <span class="detail-text" style="white-space: normal; color: #666;">{{paymentMethod}}</span>
                                </div>
                                
                                <div class="detail-row price-row">
                                    <span class="detail-icon"><img src="https://api.rosedesvins.co/v1/web/image/total%20amount" alt="Price"></span>
                                    <span class="detail-text price-text">{{totalPrice}}</span>
                                </div>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                </div>
                
                <p class="description">
                    {{serviceDescription}}
                </p>
                
                {{#if additionalNotes}}
                <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px; margin-top: 20px;">
                    <strong style="color: #3A7B59;">Notes particuli√®res de l'invit√©:</strong><br>
                    <span style="color: #666;">{{additionalNotes}}</span>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                
                {{#if eventLocation}}
                <div style="background-color: #f0f8f5; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px; margin-top: 20px;">
                    <div style="display: flex; align-items: center;">
                        <span style="margin-right: 10px;"><img src="https://api.rosedesvins.co/v1/web/image/location" alt="Location" width="16" height="16"></span>
                        <span style="color: #3A7B59; font-weight: 600;">Lieu: {{eventLocation}}</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                
                <div class="preparation-checklist">
                    <h3>üìã Pr√©paration de l'accueil</h3>
                    <ul class="checklist">
                        <li>S√©lection et pr√©paration des vins pour la d√©gustation</li>
                        <li>Am√©nagement et ambiance du lieu d'accueil</li>
                        <li>V√©rification des demandes sp√©ciales ou restrictions alimentaires</li>
                        <li>Pr√©paration des supports d'information et de d√©gustation</li>
                        <li>Accueil chaleureux et pr√©sentation du domaine</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            {{#if domainAddress}}
            <div class="domain-address">
                <strong>{{domainName}}</strong><br>
                {{domainAddress}}
            </div>
            {{/if}}
        </div>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="footer">
            <table class="footer-table">
                <tr>
                    <td class="footer-left-cell">
                        <div class="footer-logo-container">
                            <table class="footer-logo-table">
                                <tr>
                                    <td class="footer-logo-icon-cell">
                                        <div class="footer-logo-icon">
                                            <img src="{{appLogoUrl}}" alt="Rose des Vins Logo" width="30" height="30">
                                        </div>
                                    </td>
                                    <td class="footer-logo-text-cell">
                                        <div class="footer-logo-text">Rose des Vins</div>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>
                        </div>
                    </td>
                    <td class="footer-right-cell">
                        <a href="https://rosedesvins.co/#contact" class="footer-contact" style="color: white; text-decoration: none;">Contact</a>
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
